        <abstract> 
<p>Believes <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> makes science "young, clear, elevated" but does not have the facts to prove that cumulated slight modifications could ever produce different families from common ancestors. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">2709</hi>.]</p> 
        </abstract>
